room_title: Escape room "Time Warp" by Time Escape in Seattle
room_description:
It is another day in the laboratory as your group of scientists and engineers are in the final phase of what will revolutionize the world. The company has tasked your team in creating the world’s first time machine and you are in test trials. The world has always known the company has been in the forefront for time travel and mobsters have tried to take it for their own selfish purposes.
Suddenly the alarm sounds and the mobsters have breached the security walls of the company and are already inside. The CEO calls you and tasks your team on a special mission, to travel back in time and save the time machine and the company. Use your skills and travel back in time to make sure this attack is stopped. Time is of the essence so work fast and be careful as the time machine is only in test trials and you don’t want to be trapped in a time warp.
